{"type": "article", "id": 22983, "title": "有尖顶盖子的木质首饰盒", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-29T07:08:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021257097iXeNopI4zb6UTaR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个木质首饰盒，来自瑞典设计师 Diiis 。小山一样的盖子也有展示戒指和项链的功能，揭开后有一面圆镜和圆形的小碟一样的储存空间。浅色的木材表面还有细小的纹路，让这个首饰盒格外温润，可以放在门厅、卧室等多个空间中。<a href=\"http://www.diiis.ch/products/sedo\">这里是工作室主页，</a>他们有另一款与此类似的首饰盒设计。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125707rWvptl06Be9CFDUf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125708fU41IqTwbgGi9tcS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125708bFQ8XkuUsE6vZ2dO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125709ozHK5dYpsv3UGLkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}